{"tid":1858161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第十五 藍屍老母","createTime":"2020-02-02T14:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T14:21:38.000Z","uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb676f108a4051b560fee1856b2d209332810d7","tid":1858161,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1258296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1258296&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VwPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=ff577e0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1258296</a><br />\n<br />\n本港新增一宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，總數增至15宗。最新確診的病人是72歲女子，有長期病患，是早前黃埔花園確診39歲男患者的母親，女患者昨日起入住鯉魚門公園度假村的隔離營，同日發燒及咳嗽，送入伊利沙伯醫院留醫接受隔離治療，呼吸道樣本化驗後，證實對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應，她已轉送瑪嘉烈醫院接受進一步治療，情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n衛生防護中心表示，根據病人提供的資料，她於潛伏期內沒有外遊，主要逗留在家中。病人其餘四名家居接觸者，包括媳婦、孫兒、孫女及家傭，仍在隔離營接受檢疫，沒有出現病徵。"},{"pid":"7dc43d28f0e82932a012bb7da979f16f3b610cc3","tid":1858161,"uid":54291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"本地感染?無返過支那?"},{"pid":"6764375f2a77c4dda74bea56f4a348a84809e696","tid":1858161,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7dc43d28f0e82932a012bb7da979f16f3b610cc3","tid":1858161,"uid":54291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"本地感染?無返過支那?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"是早前黃埔花園確診39歲男患者的母親"},{"pid":"f7155a47f76f8058099d12d25d0042ba67683b9d","tid":1858161,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:08:13.000Z","msg":"藍屍傳比老母<br />\nlocal野"},{"pid":"a9ded57cc49a8f30577b67651bce4b8a4dc8e7d6","tid":1858161,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3ee3c0611c430f88783a